Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:01:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we're only subject to that which we hold in mind, and in my own life, I don't get sick anymore, I don't have allergies anymore, it works very well in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, my son is going through diagnosis for high-functioning autism, he's going through that process now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.31,0:01:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm always thinking about his peculiarities and all these things that I didn't realize was a different way of being,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.40,0:01:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but now it's on my mind all the time, so my concern is, is he subject to what I hold in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.17,0:01:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If I focus, by focusing so much on his peculiarities, are they being exacerbated?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I suppose there's a certain reinforcement via suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, when you have consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because he's going through this diagnosis, and we're going to doctors, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see, he's going through a diagnostic evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this week, yeah, it's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:02:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And so it's on, but, so do I, does my mind, and not by anything I say or even do, but can my thoughts influence...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Make them better or worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're not going to make them better or worse, no, because it's karmic and physiologic and everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so if I'm thinking about a lot now, it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to change his reality, so, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember during World War II, do you know, like, hundreds of millions of people hated Hitler,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and he went right on living and thriving, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hundreds of millions of people prayed for his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He went right on drinking wine, having a lady friend, and gone to the...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was saying, like, I haven't, he hasn't been told yet, and I know the power of thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like, once I tell him you have this syndrome, does he suddenly have this syndrome?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, does...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, then he's got the syndrome by label and by reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's like being short.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:02:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Being short, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:02:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:02:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So you say, well, I'm autistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like having dyslexia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, I've got a dyslexia of a couple letters and numbers, and a number of people have dyslexia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And you reverse the letters and numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's some kind of wiring in a kid, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, to me, it's a so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Except when I write four, I write R.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When I write R, I write four.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to go back and rewrite it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two other numbers and letters I'm except, but I can't remember what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a funny ad on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something for memory problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, take...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember or something, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And forget that you have memory loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the ad, have you ever seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Take memory bite within three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:03:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget that you have memory trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that was done accidentally, but it brings me up every time I hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've forgotten that I was senile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That last comment reminds me, I'm a nutritionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I talk to people about the supplements they take, they get to the point where they're supposed to be saying ginkgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And they can never remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They always just track that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginkgo biloba, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to thank you for your elaborating on the final run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Last weekend, I was listening to your 2002 tape, and those words jumped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The tape on karma, you mentioned the final run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you for bringing that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,See, one thing after another comes up to be surrendered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Like he brought up people's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a very big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It applies to so many areas, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But that, after that, something else comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just keep surrendering stuff as it comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't have to keep asking, where am I with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You just keep going until, you know, there's nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can see that each thing is a block, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My question had to do with the spiritual will that you spoke of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think it's on the same line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In Transcending the Levels, you spoke about surrendering so that spiritual will ends up guiding your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, will is like intention, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So will is your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And intention is quite powerful, as the Heisenberg Principle demonstrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Intention already selects all the possible answers and eliminates the impossible answers just by the question they were asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you assume that you're born in order to evolve into eventually enlightenment and salvation, et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,then obviously that's what it's going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And the intentional set you mentioned today, is that aligned?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Along the same lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Intentional set is, well, I talked about a contemplative lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,By intention, then, you're prioritizing the selector system.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You have multiple choices available at one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you've done is you've set a hierarchy of value.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,By spiritual intention, you've already shifted the hierarchy so that these would be more representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's an intentional set.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,By intentional set.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He may not be looking at the dials directly, but even when he's talking to his co-pilot,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,his mind is already tracking exactly what's going on with this whole plane without necessarily linear tracking of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,His attention is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So he has a joke about something and not loses track of where he's at.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The same with spiritual intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, everything becomes just for the mill, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All of life experience gets recontextualized as to its spiritual importance or meaning or significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This pen is not writing very directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a brand new one, but it's, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is actually a personal experience question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have had a sense of my spiritual quest as long as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And somewhere in my mid-20s, I had an incredible experience that was preceded by a lot of spiritual practice
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and spending time with different teachers and going through a series of out-of-body experiences quite frequently, spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And then this experience was followed by the viewing of the auric field everywhere I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just spontaneous again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And knowing that the kundalini went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And having studied and experienced all of this stuff, I had a reverse experience that I probably spent my whole life wondering what in the world it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And so this is basically curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never found anybody who could even address this question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What question?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is what this was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,After about three months of like a spiritual hermitage of meditation every day, it is as if a.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for the.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't have a word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was like somebody took a church key, popped it in the top of my head, held a spiritual garden hose to my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and energy pulsed through my body and out through my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And it never stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I meditated, it picks up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I began using it in my body work practices.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I never knew what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this sort of came this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I thought maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,God's smiling down at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're smiling as you talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're smiling as you talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it wasn't demonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like light and energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it was my body just expanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're identifying then with your energy body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why don't you just thank God and be happy with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they come, you don't have to question it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You just say, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Parking spaces always show up right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I became atheist, agnostic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years ago, I couldn't say the word God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I found your teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was praying to God, talking to God, doing all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:09:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, I was like, I'm going to be a Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I go in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I found your teaching, I was praying to God, talking to God, doing all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing the Course now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We keep hearing about the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I have the Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was Episcopalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, mother, son, and it was all anthropomorphic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you give me a working definition or a working explanation of the Holy Spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's really got me caught up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Father, the Son, and the Holy Ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Father is the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Son is the incarnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Holy Spirit is the non-physical,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,non-linear field of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,which conveys the capacity for spiritual awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we say the person who's below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is not capable of spiritual awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't ask it of him because his brain isn't wired that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But by intention and devotion, he can shift it over to the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And now he becomes capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You might understand the Holy Spirit is the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,as the non-linear, infinite context of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's omniscient, all-knowing, and all-present,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,with beginning or end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When you pray to the Holy Spirit for a miracle,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is it gets recontextualized,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and within the recontextualization,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the miraculous appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The miracle appears spontaneously of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How else would I find where I left my socks last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:12:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did I leave anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple of weeks ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I just became really aware of how annoying mind is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and how I didn't want the distracting thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and how I didn't have to follow the thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had never been so clear on it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And while I believe I'm nowhere near the final run,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of work to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've been doing it for 2 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrendered up these thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and I lasted for about 2 days,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it was just, the energy was so great,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it was like holding back a dam,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and I couldn't do it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I stay away from that kinda practice at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let your friends know that you're into spiritual practice
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in case you come cat or dog or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let all your thoughts go,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:13:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and eventually, the mind will become thoughtless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's an knowingness that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,continues. This is when you really get to a serious run. I call this the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,final run. Your spiritual intention is aligned that you're going to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,transcend the ego no matter what. It's the no matter what that scares the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So up comes fears and thoughts and things and you constantly surrender them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,as they arise. So you end up, I was liken it to the bow of the ship, as the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,thought arises, you're already surrendering to it. It's dissolving
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,before it even breaks on the prowl as a fully formed thought. With meditation you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,can see that thinkingness is arising out of an invisible energy field. It begins
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to take progressive form. Long before you see Rover, you see dogginess. Before that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel an energy of animalness. It becomes canineness. This happens in a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:14:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,split second. Then it emerges as dogginess and then it's Rover and then
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the sad story about how poor old Rover
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,rovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We all cried and it was my sister's birthday and everything. So that's what
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,what's happening then is the ego is juicing all those thoughts. So you have
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to surrender the juice you're getting out of all that. There's entertainment. So
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to surrender the entertainment of it. Face the possibility of blank mind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and boringness and surrender each thing as it arises. And then you come to some
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,incredible states. Other doors open. They're beautiful. After a while you learn
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,how to function in the world again. But it takes a while. You don't really
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,function the way the world would like you to function.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:15:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah okay we'll move it up faster. Yeah rotate those. Let's get those legs going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah right.
