Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is it is it possible that some of the individuals here or some of you know the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,students have also been visiting the void in between no
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:17:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,no yeah I just got back from a vacation from Thailand and every yeah I know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,anyways ever since I've been back all I've been thinking about is moving there
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah and I was wondering if you would please test for me to see if it would be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,for the highest good for me to move there I don't know 5% I have permission
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can ask the name of the highest good it was served as good for him to move to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thailand was just it was the says again it was served as good
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good for him to move the dialogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you bless my mom for me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't do a client like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't bless my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:18:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't usually ask personal questions, but if they're quick and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, we read your books and watch videos by ourselves, but then we're drawn
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,lots of times to get maybe to get together in groups locally or throughout the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the best way for us to use that time together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, the tradition that I, the most successful spiritual organization
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to me is 12 Step Roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They usually read from the book, take a reading from the book, and then discuss it, or play
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,a tape of some speaker, you know, and discuss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just use something like that as a take-off place, and then you share your own personal
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,experience, observation, and education, and learning, and belief systems about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And through that sharingness, you develop a certain energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The group intention energy is quite strong, and things that you might fall back, because
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of that group energy, you won't fall back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:19:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So the traditional teaching is hang out with holy company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they have a collective spiritual energy as a group energy that is uplifting, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wanted to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I think it helps support the energy field of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen people use pendulums in their hand to calibrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think in transcending the levels, when you talked about different ways to do
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrations yourself, you mentioned that, and I wanted to know if you felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there are people that do it, and if they do it, they do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell people, don't try to calibrate low energies, don't get attracted to that which
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is evil and demonic, and start trying to calibrate it, because your pendulum is going to get
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,hit by that energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And one of your energy fields and chakras can get reversed, by the way, so don't play around
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The pendulum is not a game, and same with any kind of divination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be done for sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people play with divination, and we never hear from them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So pendulum falls more in the category of, what did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a skill, and when I say if you're going to use the pendulum, then don't start
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,investigating everything negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So the other forms that you mentioned in transcending the levels were much more reliable to use
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,than a pendulum, which is more vulnerable to being influenced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the pendulum for pendulum people, I don't recommend them to people, because they
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,always have to have some curiosity, like with your questions here, that is so hypothetical,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,having nothing to do with anything to possibly be your own spiritual destination, and you're
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,just asking it out of idle curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But often you're playing with very negative energies when you're doing that, you're trying
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to flirt with the negative and think you won't get burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not going to happen, and I know a lot of people who did with pendulums started checking
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,out other dimensions, and they really blew out and even became psychotic, so I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,recommend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with being psychotic, I mean, you can lecture at universities and make a
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,good living.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have professors after me, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them to, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I've heard the word paradigm used very much, a lot, a lot more in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,lately than ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say dimension, too, the dimension of realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my question was, could you give me a general definition of paradigm, as you normally
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,relate to it, and two, can intent, are intentions limited to the paradigm that one may be in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, paradigm is context.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say how you frame it, how you frame it, and the content then, the meaning of content
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:22:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on in what kind of a frame you're framing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a good world or a bad world, apropos of what, from what context, from the viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of the man's ego, it's a very frustrating world, full of war, and poverty, and sickness,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.63,0:22:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and disease, and death, and AIDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, from what level?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the context, then, would define, you know, what you would see as true or false, so content
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.81,0:22:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is always, the answer is always dependent on the context, and the context is dependent
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,on intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.34,0:22:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the intention does live within the paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Intention sets up the paradigm, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, how it works on the internet machine, you push in the question, you've already pre-selected
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,possible answers, by pre-selection, by the, by the, how you pose the question, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.84,0:22:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.84,0:22:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The WW thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.84,0:22:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.84,0:22:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The WW internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:22:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't perform weddings, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I only married myself once, and I regretted it, so I gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.84,0:23:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.84,0:23:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.51,0:23:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you, you become enamored and romantically in love with the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The me, me, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego, the me generation was the narcissistic consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The narcissistic consequence of falling in love with your personal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really have any questions, but I wanted to get a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.58,0:23:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.83,0:23:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The me generation was the narcissism.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.83,0:23:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, me, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.75,0:23:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're rotating through the mill here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.96,0:23:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the mill door.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.96,0:23:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.96,0:23:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the mill door.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.38,0:23:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.38,0:23:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.38,0:23:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.27,0:24:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a teacher, and I'm going to be back in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.27,0:24:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.43,0:24:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.43,0:24:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.43,0:24:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a teacher, and I'm going to be back in the classroom on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.43,0:24:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I teach a reading program, and with, in high school, there's a lot of emotional resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.43,0:24:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,because they've had so much failure, a lot of drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.43,0:24:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a technique that I could use to clear, after there's big drama, to clear the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.43,0:24:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,out of my class so that it's not contagious as the other kids come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.65,0:24:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not a good place to smudge, but.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.16,0:24:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I had considered that, but we do have some dogs that do a little, and I don't know if
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.16,0:24:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,they would pick that up as.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.16,0:24:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.19,0:24:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just blessing the place, just blessing the place is all I could think you could do, you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.19,0:24:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.34,0:24:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give a blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.34,0:24:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.34,0:24:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I also wanted to know, I use intuition a lot in kind of just real quick knowing what
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.34,0:24:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the next step is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.34,0:24:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.34,0:24:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a very, very quiet way to do the thymic thump that won't be revealed to the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.34,0:24:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,public?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.34,0:24:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.34,0:24:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.34,0:24:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.34,0:24:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.34,0:24:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.34,0:24:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.34,0:24:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.34,0:25:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.34,0:25:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.34,0:25:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.34,0:25:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.34,0:25:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.34,0:25:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a way for me to do the thymic thump that won't be revealed to the class?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.99,0:25:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go ha-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.54,0:25:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.54,0:25:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a way that I can do that, align myself, because last time I was here I remember you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.47,0:25:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,did something and you said you were not aligned.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.34,0:25:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a real eye-opener to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.23,0:25:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I know that happens in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.99,0:25:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.99,0:25:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.99,0:25:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta clear yourself once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.99,0:25:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.99,0:25:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're gonna have to step out of the classroom, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.99,0:25:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.99,0:25:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.99,0:25:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go in the hallway and, uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.99,0:25:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well you tell them it's an ancient Indian tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.77,0:25:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.77,0:25:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.14,0:25:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I could be fired, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.44,0:25:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell them you learned it from the Wachahachis.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.83,0:25:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.50,0:25:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.49,0:25:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a warrior chant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.65,0:25:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a warrior chant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.97,0:25:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard it from a doctor at a lecture one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.63,0:25:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a warrior chant from the Wachahachis.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.69,0:25:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.15,0:25:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.19,0:25:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just ordained you as a teacher of the Wachahachis.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.95,0:26:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins and Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.91,0:26:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.13,0:26:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.17,0:26:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd just like to ask you a question about the celestial realms.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.23,0:26:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Once a spirit travels to the celestial realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.23,0:26:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,do they always come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.75,0:26:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,or do they have an option to stay there?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.58,0:26:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.28,0:26:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Brotherhood stays there for eons,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.97,0:26:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and some may stay there for a great long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.26,0:26:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Once in a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.91,0:26:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.06,0:26:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.03,0:26:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Broccoli?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.18,0:26:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.55,0:26:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Broccoli doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.88,0:26:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Broccoli's talking all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.18,0:26:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.70,0:26:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.24,0:26:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.33,0:26:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, her latest thing, she says,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.05,0:26:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,uh, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.44,0:26:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what's the one you can get a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.72,0:26:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you get a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.00,0:26:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.64,0:26:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to work, get a job, she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.25,0:26:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't take any sob sister stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.33,0:26:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to work, get a job, go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.20,0:26:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.83,0:27:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She tells everybody, get a job, go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.88,0:27:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's hysterical.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.85,0:27:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.84,0:27:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you familiar with the authors,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.47,0:27:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerry and Esther Hicks and Abraham?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.45,0:27:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you familiar with Edgar Cayce?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.15,0:27:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.99,0:27:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How does he calibrate, as far as...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.50,0:27:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think around 5.30 he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.69,0:27:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.19,0:27:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.36,0:27:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.26,0:27:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He brought us a lot of very good information.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.22,0:27:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Which they used in that clinic down below, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.81,0:27:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the name of the clinic that used the Cayce remedies?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.08,0:27:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.10,0:27:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the name of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.48,0:27:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget the name of the clinic, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.50,0:27:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A-R-E.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.27,0:27:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A-R-E, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.22,0:27:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Research and Enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.83,0:27:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.04,0:27:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I would like to thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.17,0:27:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your teachings and your books have had a tremendous influence
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.73,0:28:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,on my contextualization of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.88,0:28:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.85,0:28:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You said, we gravitate to and attract to what we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.75,0:28:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And what we are is not different from individual to individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.70,0:28:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it different?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.51,0:28:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And why do we end up at different levels?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.68,0:28:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,To what we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.68,0:28:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We gravitate to those who are about our same level,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.92,0:28:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that see life, experience reality, define reality the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.45,0:28:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And we stay there?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.47,0:28:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say you gravitate to your infinite...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.08,0:28:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Potentiality in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.93,0:28:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're attracted to that which you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.00,0:28:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go out on the playground, you play with those who are like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.81,0:28:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.48,0:28:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's all I mean by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.16,0:28:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're into chess, you sit with the chess players.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.09,0:28:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're into wrestling, you play with the wrestlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.29,0:29:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So you gravitate to that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.40,0:29:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the way the various dimensions of heaven are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.42,0:29:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When you leave the body, you gravitate to that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.61,0:29:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And is evolution possible at that level?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.11,0:29:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.90,0:29:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What would be the point to reincarnate if you could evolve there?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.44,0:29:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If everything is in the celestial realm, is there like 600?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.94,0:29:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you going to forgive?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.22,0:29:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't got any enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.25,0:29:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even think that way, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.83,0:29:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you go beyond 600?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.81,0:29:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get stalled out at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.57,0:29:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember the bliss of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.18,0:29:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.01,0:29:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's total.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.66,0:29:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's satisfying.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.81,0:29:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.66,0:29:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no motivation to continue any further,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.35,0:29:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,nor is there even the realization that there is such a thing as further.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.88,0:29:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So there is a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.98,0:29:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To stay there forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.24,0:29:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there is a preordained karmic knowingness or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.00,0:29:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I could have stayed in the bliss state.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.11,0:29:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And for some reason I chose to go beyond it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.44,0:30:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I found beyond bliss was even greater states, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.81,0:30:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Satchitananda is enough for most people, 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.72,0:30:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And most of the people who get there will leave the body, 50% anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.13,0:30:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in a bliss state, you need nothing more, including the physical body, and you leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.54,0:30:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if the world and karma is otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.25,0:30:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,then somebody will insist that you get up and walk around or eat something,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.30,0:30:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or they'll pull you back in the world, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.16,0:30:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.29,0:30:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.85,0:30:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And the entity is over 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.29,0:30:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they entities still?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.42,0:30:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.38,0:30:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Entity?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.14,0:30:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an entity?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.92,0:30:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.72,0:30:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, identities, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.83,0:30:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, not really identities.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.92,0:30:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, people could be finding an identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.74,0:30:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.01,0:30:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a state.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.89,0:30:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a condition, a state.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.69,0:30:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nonlinear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.77,0:31:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't a person experiencing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.85,0:31:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The person is replaced by a condition, by an overall state, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.74,0:31:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the individual airplane disappears and there's only the cloud there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.00,0:31:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That which was an airplane dissolves into the cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.28,0:31:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a person, but it's a field which has...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.89,0:31:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You become the field, you're the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.15,0:31:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the field that's the reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.25,0:31:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when you go behind the witness observer,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.89,0:31:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to the field of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.73,0:31:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.08,0:31:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a personal self anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.33,0:31:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And that helps the mankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.14,0:31:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.98,0:31:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that help mankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.00,0:31:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.79,0:31:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.44,0:31:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's time to worry about mankind, I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.83,0:31:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.25,0:31:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you'll be God.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.72,0:31:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to meet God, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.33,0:32:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender the fate of mankind to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.59,0:32:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to express my gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.64,0:32:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and thanks to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.00,0:32:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to express my gratitude and thanks to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.05,0:32:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And thankfulness to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.29,0:32:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a great gift to all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.66,0:32:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the blessings and opportunity and fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.05,0:32:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to read all of your books
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.20,0:32:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and watch a few of your DVDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.66,0:32:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel greatly helped
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.22,0:32:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and immensely blessed by your teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.61,0:32:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and by your guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.83,0:32:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.42,0:32:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd just like to thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.28,0:32:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.17,0:32:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.82,0:32:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you do me honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.16,0:32:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I honor you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.57,0:33:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no substitute for sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.25,0:33:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sincerity speaks for itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.61,0:33:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.92,0:33:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.83,0:33:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great honor to be here
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.29,0:33:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in your presence, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.96,0:33:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.68,0:33:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You said potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.35,0:33:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,manifested into actuality
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.33,0:33:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,by the power of the context
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.11,0:33:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,when the conditions are appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.74,0:33:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When the conditions are right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.03,0:33:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And one of the conditions can be intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.51,0:33:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See, intention is one of the conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.24,0:33:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is power of intention
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.40,0:33:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,propelled or directly proportional
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.11,0:33:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to the willingness to surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.33,0:33:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the conditions, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.01,0:33:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.94,0:33:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.14,0:33:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it proportional?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.35,0:33:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it propelled by willingness to surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.94,0:33:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it propelled by the willingness to surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.16,0:33:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.66,0:33:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.16,0:33:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.27,0:33:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the willingness to surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.20,0:33:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's always replaced by something greater
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.05,0:33:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,than that which you surrendered.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.82,0:33:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.57,0:33:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And where I come from,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.18,0:33:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you show reverence and regard
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.51,0:33:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,not by shake hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.38,0:33:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,by prostration.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.48,0:34:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you allow me to prostrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.27,0:34:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to touch your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.75,0:34:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.85,0:34:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.88,0:34:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.48,0:34:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.28,0:34:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand from India, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.26,0:34:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tradition,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.71,0:34:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,cultural tradition
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.50,0:34:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,by which she acknowledges the blessing, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.71,0:34:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's a gift to me from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.61,0:34:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.11,0:34:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Marks there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.53,0:34:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move any bookmarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.26,0:34:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to find those places again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.26,0:34:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.07,0:34:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my question, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.15,0:34:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.67,0:34:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I understand the,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.28,0:34:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.48,0:34:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.59,0:34:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the notes in,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.21,0:34:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in your later books, right,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.71,0:34:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have much success
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.30,0:34:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,with testing people under 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.88,0:34:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Success with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.86,0:35:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you test somebody who's under 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.86,0:35:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not successful when you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.07,0:35:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.92,0:35:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.75,0:35:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.28,0:35:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But when they try to do kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.19,0:35:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not able.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.09,0:35:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.92,0:35:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're not devoted to truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.44,0:35:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.84,0:35:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get a single one of them
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.63,0:35:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to, to disengage their narcissistic intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.94,0:35:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.48,0:35:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,God knows what kind of an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.05,0:35:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you could get out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.44,0:35:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.28,0:35:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they're so brainwashed to prove everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.01,0:35:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.36,0:35:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll lie to their mother
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.40,0:35:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to win a vote, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.63,0:35:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.80,0:35:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.30,0:35:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wanted to clarify that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.34,0:35:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,because I thought you meant maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.57,0:35:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.98,0:35:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because I test people under 200 all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.26,0:35:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and it works fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.07,0:35:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.63,0:35:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's no problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.05,0:35:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.46,0:35:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.84,0:35:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be able to use it on,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.30,0:35:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.23,0:35:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,half the population in the United States,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.59,0:35:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.94,0:35:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you could use it on them,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.65,0:35:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but they couldn't use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.51,0:35:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.11,0:35:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.48,0:35:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.88,0:35:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.36,0:35:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.88,0:35:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.03,0:35:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.09,0:35:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to prostrate, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.03,0:35:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.15,0:35:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.19,0:36:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.96,0:36:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.32,0:36:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.73,0:36:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hindu culture,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.94,0:36:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the culture from India,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.17,0:36:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it is symbolic.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.76,0:36:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets the feet of the teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.01,0:36:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's happened all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.71,0:36:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In Oxford,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.26,0:36:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they gave them a good saving.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.01,0:36:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cultural.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.75,0:36:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like in Korea,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.51,0:36:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.63,0:36:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in Korea,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.44,0:36:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a spiritual gesture, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.28,0:36:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Dr. Akhundzai,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.34,0:36:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for some practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.61,0:36:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I had in mind a mantra or something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.86,0:36:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to calm my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.26,0:36:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,particularly when I want to go to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.82,0:36:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,or something's aggravating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.19,0:36:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was intrigued in the power of the truthiest
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.98,0:36:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,full-terrated om at 720.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.76,0:36:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So I kind of tried that for a little bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.28,0:36:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seems to me I got to make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.76,0:36:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you make silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.71,0:36:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You make a sound silently in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.84,0:37:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Om namah shivaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.50,0:37:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Om namah shivaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.11,0:37:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You intone it silently,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.53,0:37:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,not vocally.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.65,0:37:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried I a little bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.44,0:37:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking that was at a thousand,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.88,0:37:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seemed a little egotistical.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.61,0:37:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just do om namah shivaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.86,0:37:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.84,0:37:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.75,0:37:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.15,0:37:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a picture too?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.26,0:37:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.46,0:37:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shivaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.51,0:37:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.48,0:37:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.07,0:37:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Makkananda, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.42,0:37:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was with him for six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.50,0:37:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then you're asking me a question,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.00,0:37:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,dumb head, to go back and...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.05,0:37:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're high level.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.01,0:37:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.67,0:37:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.67,0:37:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good om namah shivaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.34,0:38:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My question has to do with the relative field
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.94,0:38:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that was on your chart,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.53,0:38:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,with the general field,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.82,0:38:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the proximate field, I believe is the term.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.01,0:38:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the proximate, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.78,0:38:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.32,0:38:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's like local conditions, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.32,0:38:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.88,0:38:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Given that time and space
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.71,0:38:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,are linear concepts, position, proximate, how,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.76,0:38:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and why is it important to the spiritual process?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.80,0:38:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.84,0:38:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the thing integrous or not, truthful or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.63,0:38:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on the situation, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.67,0:38:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.71,0:38:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And even a court of law.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.51,0:38:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's also called situational ethics.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.05,0:38:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth or the untruth, the rightness or wrongness,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.40,0:38:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on one, what conditions, what conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.94,0:38:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,what were the prevailing conditions in the person's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.23,0:38:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the country in general, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.44,0:38:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.73,0:38:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To take certain moves depends on whether or not
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.01,0:38:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,your country's at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.21,0:38:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That totally changes the whole context.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.11,0:38:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So what I can say in times of peace would be,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.48,0:39:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, a felony in times of war, let's say, you know, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.57,0:39:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.19,0:39:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Or vice versa, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.86,0:39:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.94,0:39:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here for the grace of the guru,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.21,0:39:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so I wanted to make sure I had a good dose.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.01,0:39:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.34,0:39:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I figured I'd better come up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.13,0:39:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dollar for a big dose.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.53,0:39:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A big dose.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.01,0:39:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I left my purse back there, so I'll have to go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.21,0:39:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.21,0:39:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just wanted to ask exactly how does that work,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.86,0:39:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the grace of the guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.98,0:39:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's called the silent transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.98,0:39:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's traditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.05,0:39:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The knowingness that I had at the final moment
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.57,0:39:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,came as a silent knowingness, not verbal, not from memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.94,0:39:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a radiance from the aura, having been in the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.01,0:39:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of a very high teacher at one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.98,0:40:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field picks it up, the frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.82,0:40:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The nearest corollary would be the old pendulum one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.17,0:40:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You put, you know, if you put pendulum clocks on a wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.38,0:40:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,they will all begin to move together, you know that,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.90,0:40:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and heighten or whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.65,0:40:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the frequency vibration of the aura
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.26,0:40:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is picked up by your aura by virtue of your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.65,0:40:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your intention, you instantly pick up and pull into your own aura
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.38,0:40:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.01,0:40:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Within that aura is a great deal of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.21,0:40:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say encompassed in a silent nonverbal knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.09,0:40:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,experiential and subjective, therefore it can't be conveyed verbally.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.94,0:40:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be conveyed verbally.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.57,0:40:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.57,0:40:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the energy field out of which true authority arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.21,0:40:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The true authority is one who has experienced it and been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.34,0:40:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So Jesus the Christ has the power of salvation,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.61,0:40:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,having been there, and he has within his aura the power of that energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.21,0:41:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,just as the Buddha had the power of enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.13,0:41:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,which has been transmitted down through the thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.13,0:41:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.40,0:41:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you very much. I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.59,0:41:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the silent transmission, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.59,0:41:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It occurs in the silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.65,0:41:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.69,0:41:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.94,0:41:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.98,0:41:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.01,0:41:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like my friend when I take the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.11,0:41:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have young teenage, or young adult children.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.11,0:41:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I get concerned about choices that they might make for their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.51,0:41:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I surrender it to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.59,0:41:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.63,0:41:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The choices?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.67,0:41:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.67,0:42:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.67,0:42:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that help them?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.67,0:42:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is that only making me feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.75,0:42:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't surrender it to God because you're trying to control them by surrendering it to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.51,0:42:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.55,0:42:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.59,0:42:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So is there anything that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.63,0:42:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To truly surrender it by God, they've got their own karmic trip to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.67,0:42:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And whatever they do, they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.44,0:42:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do the best you can as a parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.13,0:42:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And up to then, it's up to their karma, their options.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.13,0:42:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.28,0:42:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Their destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.28,0:42:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happens, happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.28,0:42:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And whatever happens, happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.28,0:42:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.28,0:42:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And it doesn't make any difference in the long run which way it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.28,0:42:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.38,0:42:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.38,0:42:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.38,0:42:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.38,0:42:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to do what you tell them to do anyway, because you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.34,0:42:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.57,0:42:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, each one has to develop their own independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.09,0:42:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.09,0:43:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They develop their own independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.90,0:43:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.90,0:43:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.90,0:43:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a professional musician.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.90,0:43:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just had a situation that happened that I wanted to ask you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.30,0:43:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to fire one of my long-time musicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.30,0:43:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering if there was a more integrous way that I handled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.26,0:43:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a behavior that was detrimental to the band reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.23,0:43:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just wrote him a letter thanking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.28,0:43:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had to point out the incidences of his behavior, because I guess it was part of me
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.76,0:43:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that wanted him to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.80,0:43:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Be specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.80,0:43:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.90,0:43:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.90,0:43:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is, is there a more integrous way to have handled it where I didn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.90,0:43:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to point out his negative behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.90,0:43:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.88,0:43:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.76,0:43:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.84,0:43:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.84,0:43:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,To go with an explanation is loving in a way, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.86,0:43:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's not just arbitrary.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.86,0:44:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And it might help him grow, see where shortcomings are.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.86,0:44:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.86,0:44:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gave him some honest feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.86,0:44:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it didn't work out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.86,0:44:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you might also, you know, it's whether they can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.86,0:44:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Very often, you just have to tell them, you're gone, and I just can't tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.86,0:44:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because no matter what you tell them, they're going to use that as an ammo to fight back at you,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.86,0:44:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,fire back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.94,0:44:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's an intuitive option.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.94,0:44:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you which is the best way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.86,0:44:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Circumstances are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.26,0:44:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's better to part and tell them, frankly, I can't give you an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.26,0:44:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the way it is, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.26,0:44:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Other times, you try to give an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.42,0:44:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot of people will then use the explanation to further attack you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.42,0:44:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and do the very thing that you're letting them go for.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.42,0:44:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in this particular situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.42,0:44:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't give them a lot of rope, generally.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.42,0:44:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd try to give you as little rope as possible and tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.42,0:44:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, it's because it's just not working out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.42,0:44:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.42,0:44:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.30,0:44:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.30,0:44:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In hindsight, that may have been the better way because he's in such denial that he didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.30,0:45:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, it depends on how you see yourself, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.30,0:45:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.30,0:45:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You save yourself a lot of static if you tell them that's just the way it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.30,0:45:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't really get into it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.09,0:45:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.09,0:45:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.82,0:45:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you give reasons, you're opening up a box of worms a lot of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.82,0:45:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a Pepsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.01,0:45:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The new president of PepsiCo is a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.26,0:45:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.30,0:45:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Head of the second largest corporation in America?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.26,0:45:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.26,0:45:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Woman, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.26,0:45:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They've come all the way to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.26,0:45:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget glass ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.69,0:45:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned that at first you were surprised when people addressed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.65,0:45:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.65,0:45:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're not limited to this body and mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.01,0:46:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think you also said that have calibrated that it's a benefit for us to be in your physical presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.46,0:46:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wondered if you would comment further on that sort of paradox.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.69,0:46:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the paradox?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.86,0:46:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The person, see, when you're not the body anymore, you notice everybody's talking to the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.11,0:46:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,because you don't, it's like you're more like space.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.11,0:46:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And you wonder who are they talking to, because it's like you're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.11,0:46:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're talking to a body over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.11,0:46:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not even there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.40,0:46:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not identified with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.40,0:46:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And people are talking to this body, and it dawned on me, oh, they think that that's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.40,0:46:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot the world presumes that the body is where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.36,0:46:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And they speak to the body, because they think that's who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.36,0:46:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can be out of body, and they're in the bedroom, you know, talking to the body in the bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.19,0:46:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're not even there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.19,0:46:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up in the corner of the room, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.19,0:46:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of comical.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.28,0:46:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.28,0:47:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they think that's you down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.28,0:47:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.28,0:47:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to remind yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.28,0:47:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have to tell them, get down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.38,0:47:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.38,0:47:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That is funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.34,0:47:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,At dinner time, I've disappeared, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.34,0:47:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.36,0:47:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's not answerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.36,0:47:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.53,0:47:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a readjustment period.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.63,0:47:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.63,0:47:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.63,0:47:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.63,0:47:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.63,0:47:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As one transcends the levels of consciousness, is there any responsibility or importance to share, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.63,0:47:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual truths or insights with others?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.25,0:47:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's your option.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.21,0:47:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people belong to spiritual groups and share, you know, what the experience was.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.21,0:48:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That encourages others to choose that direction or try that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.34,0:48:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's a lot of value in sharing, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.34,0:48:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The big traditional ones like AA, sharing is a big part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.34,0:48:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I was scared of this, and I began to see it this way, and then I saw it that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.94,0:48:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and then when I saw it this way, it didn't seem so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.94,0:48:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other guy says, hey, you know, that's sort of what I did, only I saw it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.90,0:48:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the next week they come back and, you know, they share what went on that week when they tried that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.90,0:48:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,By God, I worked that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.90,0:48:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah, there's a lot of encouragement in group sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.09,0:48:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How about with friends and loved ones, family members?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.09,0:48:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.09,0:48:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.09,0:48:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It would depend on the receptivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.09,0:48:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people might think you're a wacko, so you've got to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.05,0:48:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.05,0:48:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.63,0:48:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't come out of the blue with it, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.63,0:48:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see angels flying around your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.11,0:48:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.19,0:48:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.11,0:49:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.94,0:49:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Best to keep certain things to yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.94,0:49:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.53,0:49:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.53,0:49:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.53,0:49:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, in the 12-step programs, there is the subject of powerlessness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.59,0:49:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and powerlessness over specific things, but sometimes it is said that we are powerless over everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.90,0:49:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.90,0:49:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.86,0:49:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All power is God.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.86,0:49:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All power is God, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.86,0:49:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, I guess I'm confused because I read in some literature that what we hold in mind tends to manifest, or we can visualize the future and manifest it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.86,0:49:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just wondering if it's best to...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.86,0:49:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the contradiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.86,0:49:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just wondering if it's best...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.86,0:49:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.86,0:50:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.86,0:50:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That means the will.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.86,0:50:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It means seeing yourself as cause, that you have the power to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.82,0:50:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When you hold something in mind, you're not making it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.23,0:50:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sharing the water, you know, you're creating a place, but the water is going where it's going out of gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.23,0:50:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not making the water run.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.23,0:50:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you hold a vision of what you consider to be optional, the likelihood is greater that that will be manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.46,0:50:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But just by intention, the fact that you selected it is already imposing intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.46,0:50:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,By virtue of the Heisenberg principle, by virtue of the mathematics of advanced theoretical physics,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.42,0:50:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you increase the likelihood by your choice that the choice will be chosen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.42,0:50:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zeno effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.42,0:50:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The more often you make an optional choice, the more likely that is to be chosen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.86,0:50:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, that's part of intention set.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.86,0:50:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the more often you choose to forgive someone and ask God to see it differently, that becomes the predominant response pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.86,0:51:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Is it best to cease thinking about the future altogether and just leave it to God?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.61,0:51:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the future. What future are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.61,0:51:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any future.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.57,0:51:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't got any future. I can read it in your aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.57,0:51:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only going to go from the moment, from now to now to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.57,0:51:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to have any future.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.57,0:51:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmically, you didn't inherit any future.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.57,0:51:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You only inherited nowness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.57,0:51:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to go from now to now to now to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.26,0:51:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Other people have to hang out and wait for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.26,0:51:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've been saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.26,0:51:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.26,0:51:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Saved for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.23,0:51:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have to handle this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.03,0:51:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, this building could collapse in one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.03,0:51:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.03,0:51:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always going to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.03,0:51:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.03,0:51:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Call your mother first, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.21,0:51:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear the next big, okay, Mom, the building is falling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.21,0:52:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't kick it to heaven without a cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.78,0:52:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Call in the big guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.34,0:52:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Call letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.30,0:52:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.30,0:52:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus said, blessed are the humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.13,0:52:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just like you to say in your words what you, a definition of humility.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.13,0:52:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the letting go of the narcissistic, the narcissistic investment in the mind, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.80,0:52:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Humility is the willingness to surrender all to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.92,0:52:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And eventually, to surrender the notion there's an independent individual I that is motivating and etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.92,0:52:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, that is cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.05,0:52:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the ultimate vanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.05,0:52:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, constantly surrendering will eventually take you to the narcissistic core of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.05,0:53:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when you surrender that, you go into a real state of bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.05,0:53:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you see everything is beautiful and perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.05,0:53:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's nothing you have to do or become.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.46,0:53:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I understood the pendulum is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.42,0:53:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't do any research on anything under 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.55,0:53:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I, I, I don't advise it, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.73,0:53:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The angels fear to tread there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.73,0:53:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.73,0:53:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because why?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.21,0:53:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's morbid curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.21,0:53:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know how awful, awful is?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.21,0:53:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to check out hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.53,0:53:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to check out hell without getting burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.53,0:53:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I advise people don't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.53,0:53:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be tempted by the drama of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.38,0:53:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.38,0:53:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.34,0:53:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you want to climb the highest mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.44,0:53:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,make note of the fact that 176 people have died there already doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.61,0:53:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.61,0:54:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.67,0:54:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have a sanity check on all the people that want to climb the highest mountains in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.21,0:54:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how many would pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.46,0:54:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi doctor, hi Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.09,0:54:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't been here for a while because we have been traveling around, my husband and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.09,0:54:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are coming from Oregon.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.09,0:54:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just thought about giving you this little bitty
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.05,0:54:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary and Barry jam just for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.05,0:54:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're in a jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.59,0:54:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.98,0:54:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.98,0:54:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say hello and say thank you very much for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.98,0:54:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're here from Oregon now, huh? Oregon?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.98,0:54:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, we're going farther up to Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.98,0:54:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're staying up for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.98,0:54:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We are staying in Oregon.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.94,0:54:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to Mexico now to visit my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.94,0:54:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that's the other direction, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.94,0:55:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.94,0:55:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I just wanted to really express my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.94,0:55:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Before reading Power Versus Force, I used to suffer from anxiety disorder and panic attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.94,0:55:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after working in a 12-step program for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.94,0:55:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And it happened in 2001, the first time that I got Power Versus Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.90,0:55:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.90,0:55:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I haven't suffered one panic attack at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.90,0:55:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.90,0:55:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've also seen people, I know people, some girls that I know that live in Texas suffering from eating disorders.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.90,0:55:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,After watching the tape of losing weight, they were completely cured to this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.90,0:55:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.09,0:55:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.09,0:55:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.09,0:55:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.09,0:55:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.09,0:56:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also would like to just say thank you for being the lighthouse and to also prostrate if that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.09,0:56:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.09,0:56:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.09,0:56:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.23,0:56:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.61,0:56:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.55,0:56:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.78,0:56:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.78,0:56:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.82,0:56:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.82,0:56:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.50,0:56:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.05,0:56:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.48,0:56:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.48,0:56:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to answer this?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.61,0:56:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.61,0:56:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.69,0:56:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to make the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.78,0:56:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.78,0:56:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.13,0:56:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.13,0:56:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.40,0:56:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Would serve the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.40,0:57:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The program he's holding in mind, he wants us to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.26,0:57:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.26,0:57:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the program that you're holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.26,0:57:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.26,0:57:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.26,0:57:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.26,0:57:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.90,0:57:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep it to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.57,0:57:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What he's holding in mind would serve the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.57,0:57:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.96,0:57:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.82,0:57:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.03,0:57:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.03,0:57:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night as we were driving out here, a group from Texas, we were listening to a tape of someone reading quotes from Nisargadatta Maharaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.17,0:57:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And one of the quotes was that trying to help others, there's no value in trying to help others because in reality there is no others.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.80,0:58:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was curious, some of us kind of had trouble with that because we're in recovery and that's kind of the part of the goal of 12 Step Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.15,0:58:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The goal of 12 Step Groups is to help others.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.84,0:58:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was curious if you could recontextualize that for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.65,0:58:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,See, each level is only true at its own level.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.28,0:58:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not true at the level that you're experiencing reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.53,0:58:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It would become just an intellectual belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.53,0:58:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.26,0:58:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.55,0:58:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I'd like to thank you all again for everything in the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.55,0:58:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I've felt the energy and how it's helped me to arrive here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.51,0:58:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And also felt the energy to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.65,0:58:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.59,0:58:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And also felt the energy to go back to my AA group at home and seen it kind of swarm through the people there and just lift them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.55,0:58:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.55,0:59:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question has to do with a family member.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.78,0:59:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother is very ill and it seems as though she's in a very negative state.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.01,0:59:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And it gets overwhelming to be around her because of the energy that she puts off is very negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.01,0:59:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's like you're trying to draw me into misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.05,0:59:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just kind of wondered if you could maybe recontextualize it or how I can deal with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.01,0:59:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So can you just avoid it?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.30,0:59:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of hard to avoid my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.30,0:59:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you living with your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.30,0:59:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.30,0:59:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 27.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.30,0:59:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't live with her, but I live in the same city with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.30,0:59:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And she is very ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.30,0:59:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else is there to look after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.30,0:59:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.30,0:59:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the only caretaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.30,0:59:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.30,0:59:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's at a point where she can care for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.30,0:59:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Does?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.59,0:59:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But she goes to the hospital regularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.59,0:59:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.46,0:59:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She has post-operative problems from colorectal cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.61,0:59:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.61,0:59:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's in remission and she's in a colostomy bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.61,0:59:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.61,1:00:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But the misery that she's in, it seems like, is just overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.61,1:00:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative projections on everybody's out to get me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.61,1:00:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody likes me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.61,1:00:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.61,1:00:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, call the minister and tell her after you talk to the minister.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.61,1:00:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.61,1:00:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.96,1:00:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to sit down and draw a line.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.96,1:00:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just draw a line.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.05,1:00:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I tried to offer.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.05,1:00:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want somebody to mess with me just because they're in a miserable state.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.09,1:00:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.05,1:00:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.05,1:00:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, she can play around and help, but I'm not going to join.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.05,1:00:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.05,1:00:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.05,1:00:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think you've got to throw back to herself what her responsibility is to herself and to others.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.05,1:00:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.26,1:00:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And the narcissistic self-indulgence and suffering and playing it for all it's worth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.30,1:00:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I would refuse it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.30,1:00:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.30,1:00:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And just one more thing I thought you could answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.30,1:00:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you make your life a living prayer?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.90,1:00:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You practice what you read.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.90,1:00:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You practice what you read.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.50,1:00:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You practice it at all times.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.46,1:00:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you read a sentence.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.46,1:00:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.46,1:01:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And where can you practice that?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.46,1:01:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to institute it and practice it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.46,1:01:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say thank you to every clerk who's, you know, you ask somebody for a phone number.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.00,1:01:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She gives it to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.00,1:01:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You say thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.00,1:01:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You just begin by acknowledging other people.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.00,1:01:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you do that, as I've said, people will faint.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.00,1:01:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll just drop their face like, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.00,1:01:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they've made change for 150 people.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.38,1:01:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.42,1:01:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, gee, thank you for making change.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.38,1:01:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They go, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.38,1:01:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just begin by radiating some kind of gratitude towards all of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.51,1:01:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Reflect back that, you know, everybody is contributing to everybody else's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.05,1:01:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And be as loving, unconditionally loving as you can towards everyone at all times.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.05,1:01:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.11,1:01:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.11,1:01:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Intention begins to transform it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.36,1:01:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And the opportunities open up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.51,1:01:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for a...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.51,1:02:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the mic.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.15,1:02:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.15,1:02:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.15,1:02:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.15,1:02:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.15,1:02:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nervous, so I'm going to be the only...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.15,1:02:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm reading.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.15,1:02:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.15,1:02:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a doctor's handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.55,1:02:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.55,1:02:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.55,1:02:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.55,1:02:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the gist.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.55,1:02:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.55,1:02:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You were talking in the morning about repeating a mantra over and over, leading to bliss,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.55,1:02:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,God consciousness, enlightenment, and then silence, connecting with God.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.51,1:02:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm a person who's been chanting Nam-myoho-renge-kyo many, many, many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.51,1:02:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.51,1:02:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted you to talk more about doing a daily practice, you know, to reach enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.51,1:02:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it sounds like you go off into a state of bliss, but we live in the mundane world.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.51,1:02:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel a need to recharge my batteries.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.46,1:03:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just want you to talk a little bit about a daily practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.46,1:03:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Prayer, meditation, chanting, whatever it is that people do.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.73,1:03:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the daily practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.13,1:03:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You pick out something and you use that as a sort of a primary tool.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.17,1:03:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,To see the beauty of everything by intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.17,1:03:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.17,1:03:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,To ask the Holy Spirit for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.17,1:03:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,To see everything as it is in truth rather than perception.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.17,1:03:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,To let go and to change things as they arise.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.17,1:03:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.21,1:03:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to control them.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.36,1:03:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To let go valuing what people think about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.36,1:03:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To stop looking for people's approval.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.36,1:03:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Any one of those, if you just, you see, it's persistence.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.36,1:03:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the spiritual work is persistence.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.73,1:03:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Persistence.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.86,1:03:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you walk by the little beetle on his back and you fail to turn him over, it bothers you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.01,1:03:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.01,1:03:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When it bothers you, you know you're making progress.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.80,1:04:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're the whole way, whether he survives or not, it's God's problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.84,1:04:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how you knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.90,1:04:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a lot of beetles lying on their backs lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.90,1:04:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm getting a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.90,1:04:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At one level, it's a mistake to not stop and help the beetle.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.90,1:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At another level, it's a mistake to stop and help the beetle.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.90,1:04:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's, each level sees it differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.28,1:04:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.84,1:04:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, and using some spiritual jargon, you say, well, there's no separate beagle, so there's no beetle to save, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.65,1:04:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I often think that becomes a belief system.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.86,1:04:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't like to hear people quote that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.38,1:04:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.38,1:04:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.38,1:04:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.38,1:04:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.38,1:04:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all one what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.36,1:05:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your books and your lectures, they've had a profound effect on my life in the past year.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.36,1:05:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And really, they were the spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.36,1:05:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing that basically got me on the spiritual path is reading your books.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.36,1:05:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.36,1:05:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've stated frequently that,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.53,1:05:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,540 or unconditional love has the power, if you reach that level, has the power to cure whatever ills you or whatever disease it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.48,1:05:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.48,1:05:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at 540.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.48,1:05:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But 540 is a level of healingness of incurable conditions, AA, A Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.32,1:05:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,540 and up, that which is impossible becomes possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.32,1:05:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a transformation to a different dimension of possibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.32,1:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.32,1:05:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.28,1:05:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've suffered from chronic and clinical depression.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.28,1:05:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.28,1:05:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For years, actually.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.57,1:05:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.57,1:06:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I find what I read from you very helpful, also other things.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.69,1:06:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder, as a psychoanalyst, what role, I'm starting psychoanalysis, and I was wondering what role that plays in it, or is that emotional, what's the word?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.69,1:06:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, everything is physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.69,1:06:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.65,1:06:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So you should approach it from all three.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.65,1:06:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean psychoanalysis, so?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.65,1:06:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about physical, mental, and spiritual, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.65,1:06:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.65,1:06:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.65,1:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Physical, there's entity presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.65,1:06:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of them work in a miraculous way.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.65,1:06:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They certainly are worth a worthy try.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.65,1:06:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is mental, and by mental, it's also neurophysiology in the brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.65,1:06:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So trying to affect the brain, physical, mental, and it's also spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.65,1:06:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So I believe you should attack everything on all three levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.65,1:06:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The psychological, the psychological.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.65,1:06:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The psychological, the spiritual, and the biochemical.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.30,1:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.30,1:06:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All three.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.38,1:06:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And then if we're in due time, you could probably drop off, diminish the biochemical.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.38,1:06:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.38,1:07:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, these things are very cyclic.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.38,1:07:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have a cycle of 10 or 20 years where depressions are frequent or overwhelming, and then they will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.38,1:07:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have a period where they're there for five years, and then they disappear for 10 years, and then it'll recycle back for a year.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.38,1:07:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's also cyclic.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.78,1:07:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And all three.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.78,1:07:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All three levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.42,1:07:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.42,1:07:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And is there a role for 12-step groups in this process?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.42,1:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know any 12-step groups for depression.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.42,1:07:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't either.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.42,1:07:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just was wondering if they...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.42,1:07:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The nearest thing would be A Course in Miracles group, because that's recovery from almost everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.42,1:07:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.63,1:07:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.63,1:07:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.63,1:07:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also a group called Recovery Inc.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.63,1:07:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if they're still around as they used to be years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.63,1:07:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They addressed depression directly.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.25,1:07:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.42,1:07:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.30,1:07:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty common emotional illness.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.30,1:08:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It afflicts one-third of Americans at some time in their life to a serious degree.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.26,1:08:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not depressed, it's because you're not reading the paper lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.98,1:08:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Too dumb to not have a good...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.98,1:08:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're smart enough, you do get sort of depressed a little about human life, its condition, its limitations, the traps, the ambiguities.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.05,1:08:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you for all your options.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.05,1:08:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.01,1:08:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Try it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.01,1:08:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Be depressed about the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.01,1:08:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.10,1:08:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.10,1:08:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry about the Okenduka Indians or somebody that you're in trouble with or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.59,1:08:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I just made that up, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.59,1:08:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.59,1:08:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.59,1:08:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Project your worry onto something human, but not the personal human, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.52,1:08:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.71,1:08:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.71,1:08:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was a good pen.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.71,1:08:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.81,1:08:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to thank you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.81,1:08:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.81,1:09:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been a profound influence on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.81,1:09:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I find myself being pulled into legal controversies and things like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.89,1:09:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And my first response was to, you know, I can live without the money and other things that are involved.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.14,1:09:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.14,1:09:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And your writings on passivity and so forth...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.14,1:09:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.10,1:09:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...taught me that I should speak to truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.10,1:09:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.10,1:09:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up for truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.10,1:09:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up and speak to truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.10,1:09:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up for truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.10,1:09:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not win, but you at least...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.10,1:09:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.10,1:09:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.10,1:09:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Your obligation has been to tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.10,1:09:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's three or four of these things going on around me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.10,1:09:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm trying to...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.10,1:09:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a student of the Course, and I try to live by the principles of the Course as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.10,1:09:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.10,1:09:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.10,1:10:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And your advice on Psalm 91 was helpful to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.06,1:10:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.94,1:10:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not the 100% that you had on the screen there on forgiveness, but I find myself better able to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.94,1:10:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.94,1:10:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The other thing that I have meditated and contemplated is the renunciation of the fruits of my actions.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.94,1:10:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel like that helps.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.94,1:10:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.94,1:10:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But what else can you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.90,1:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What else can you tell me on this?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.90,1:10:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like you're doing very good on it so far.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.52,1:10:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst that can happen is you get totally wiped out and you're penniless.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.52,1:10:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.52,1:10:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.52,1:10:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.52,1:10:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get wiped out and totally penniless, give me a call.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.52,1:10:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.35,1:10:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if I don't ascend in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.06,1:10:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let go of the sandbags.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.06,1:10:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to float right up there, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.47,1:11:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only woe keeping you in this world.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.47,1:11:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of the woe and bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.63,1:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to let go of it all has a magical effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.00,1:11:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like fearless after that.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.48,1:11:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.51,1:11:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.67,1:11:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.97,1:11:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on one second.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.10,1:11:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is multifunction now.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.82,1:11:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably a microphone that takes your picture while you're talking to it, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.82,1:11:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes a tape recording and transmits it via the internet to the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.82,1:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Read about yourself on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.82,1:12:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.82,1:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them are in Mongolia.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.82,1:12:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it get out there?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.82,1:12:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.82,1:12:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a satellite or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.19,1:12:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the way the world is?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.19,1:12:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Complex.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.19,1:12:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.19,1:12:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc, will you lead us in a prayer of devotional non-duality?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.19,1:12:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We end up with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.69,1:12:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-duality means non-conceptual, non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.18,1:12:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In as much as it's silent, it'll have to be silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.14,1:12:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all right with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.22,1:12:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.22,1:12:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have a group silence later.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.27,1:12:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.15,1:13:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.15,1:13:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.11,1:13:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to thank the staff, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.11,1:13:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.11,1:13:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The question I have, and I'm sure this has been gone over a time or two, is there comes a time, there's a couple times it's came up to possibly calibrate family.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.11,1:13:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm kind of like not sure about doing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.11,1:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I try to stay away from that part.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.11,1:13:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We do a lot of muscle tests, my wife and I.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.46,1:13:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your take on that sort of...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.17,1:13:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be what the motivation is, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.32,1:13:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for guidance to understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.18,1:13:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's the context in which you're asking your intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.18,1:13:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If what you're angry at a person about is that they're not higher or more than what they are, then you might get relief.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.31,1:13:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You calibrate them and you find them, look, they're only 190 or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.27,1:14:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They're already at being the best that they can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.27,1:14:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can let go of your resentment.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.27,1:14:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So it would depend on what is your intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.27,1:14:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To heal, to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.61,1:14:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What would be the intention?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.61,1:14:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's also, there's been a friend of the family who was wondering about their spouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.73,1:14:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I go, no, I'm not even going there.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.73,1:14:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.73,1:14:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's what I say.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.73,1:14:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I go, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.51,1:14:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.47,1:14:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure to tread there, brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.47,1:14:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.14,1:14:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to watch out for curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.14,1:14:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Curiosity killed the cat.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.14,1:14:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And curiosity is a glamour.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.61,1:14:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I never read that, but I just realized that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.35,1:14:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Curiosity is, first of all, innate to life.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.35,1:14:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Without curiosity, humankind, we wouldn't even live.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.35,1:15:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And curiosity also takes you right over the edge.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.35,1:15:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And you get fried.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.35,1:15:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So curiosity is, on the one hand, a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.31,1:15:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, it's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.31,1:15:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of a glamour.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.92,1:15:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of a glamour.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.57,1:15:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That you have to know all about something.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.57,1:15:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've discovered you don't have to know anything about something.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.57,1:15:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrap it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.57,1:15:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I read the instructions.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.57,1:15:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.57,1:15:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I put it all back together and put it back on the shelf.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.26,1:15:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.53,1:15:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.23,1:15:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.23,1:15:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you, I've been using these prayer beads on occasion.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.30,1:15:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was hoping you might.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.26,1:15:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been eating them?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.26,1:15:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not very often.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.26,1:15:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.26,1:15:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.26,1:15:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Prayer beads, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.26,1:15:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.26,1:15:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoy them very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.26,1:15:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.26,1:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.26,1:16:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My question to you was, have you ever calibrated the fellow, Alfred Adler?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.26,1:16:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a contemporary of Jung and Freud.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.26,1:16:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.26,1:16:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be interested in doing so?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.26,1:16:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he, I can tell you right off.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.26,1:16:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Adler was, yeah, the will.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.22,1:16:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He was very important in the psychoanalytic movement.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.22,1:16:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.22,1:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I never did Adler.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.22,1:16:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he could be in the good 400.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.22,1:16:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to do Adler.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.22,1:16:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He was over 440, 450, 445.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.22,1:16:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I would guess him around 440, 445.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.51,1:16:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.51,1:16:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.51,1:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Alfred Adler was, he made a very good contribution to psychoanalytic theory.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.51,1:16:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.51,1:16:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.51,1:16:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.52,1:16:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.52,1:16:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.47,1:17:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say that since I came out here, I've been having a lot of memories from, they feel like memories from, like, ancient Rome.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.51,1:17:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I just was asking for confirmation on those.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.30,1:17:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.44,1:17:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Flashbacks?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.44,1:17:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Flashbacks.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.44,1:17:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.44,1:17:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.44,1:17:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just curious if, like, the authenticity of those, specifically since I came out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.44,1:17:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have a flashback?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.44,1:17:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was remembering times in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.44,1:17:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.44,1:17:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Times in where?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.44,1:17:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rome.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.40,1:17:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rome.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.05,1:17:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he meant your Rome.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.05,1:17:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He was having flashbacks of Rome.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.57,1:17:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're genuine.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.57,1:17:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're genuine.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.57,1:17:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.57,1:17:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.57,1:17:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of us lived in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.57,1:17:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was remembering you, so.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.57,1:17:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of us lived in Rome, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.57,1:17:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other question was, could I give you a hug?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.57,1:17:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because the back is too fragile.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.67,1:17:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.67,1:17:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.67,1:18:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.67,1:18:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.67,1:18:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can hug my hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.67,1:18:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.63,1:18:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.81,1:18:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The other bones, I don't stress them.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.53,1:18:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.61,1:18:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The bones break easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.61,1:18:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a friend hug me and broke three ribs on one side.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.10,1:18:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I went to a dancing class.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.10,1:18:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The lady went under this arm, and her head hit me and broke three ribs on that side.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.63,1:18:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends are killing me right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.18,1:18:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.18,1:18:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is work-related.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.18,1:18:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a mental health therapist, and I work with a lot of people who are on probation.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.14,1:18:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I work for committing acts of violence.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.14,1:18:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.14,1:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Specifically sexual violence.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.14,1:18:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.14,1:18:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm real interested in your work on the primitive mind and the etheric mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.14,1:18:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering if maybe I should continue.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.14,1:18:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The etheric mind and the primitive mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.14,1:19:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have been having questions about whether I should continue the work or whether it's really not going to go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.92,1:19:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What work, honey?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.92,1:19:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't quite get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.92,1:19:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean with the individual patient?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.92,1:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.92,1:19:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.07,1:19:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it depends on what kind of work.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.03,1:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm using pretty much cognitive behavioral.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.03,1:19:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.03,1:19:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,CBT, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.03,1:19:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.03,1:19:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what the results of it is in that patient group, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.55,1:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.55,1:19:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I tend to be skeptical of that group.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.47,1:19:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wondered if you could test to see if it would be for that common good if I continue this work.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.18,1:19:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should change it to something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.18,1:19:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the work you're doing contributing to the common good?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.18,1:19:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.18,1:19:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.18,1:19:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if we have permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.14,1:19:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask that here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.14,1:19:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.14,1:19:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The work she's doing is serving the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.14,1:19:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It is serving the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.17,1:19:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.47,1:19:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See, what you're dealing with is the last gaspers.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.47,1:19:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.47,1:20:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bottom of the pit.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.47,1:20:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.47,1:20:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.47,1:20:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So a lot of times when they're at the bottom of the pit, they're more approachable than when they're still halfway up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.47,1:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.10,1:20:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When they're at the bottom of the pit, they become sweetly reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.36,1:20:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when they're not at the bottom of the pit, they're still cocky.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.32,1:20:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.77,1:20:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cocky.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.77,1:20:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.77,1:20:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.93,1:20:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just let them go in the direction they go.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.80,1:20:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha said you don't have to bring anybody down because they'll bring themselves down by their own hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.80,1:20:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just wait long enough and they will hit bottom.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.80,1:20:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And when they hit bottom, they become sweetly reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.80,1:20:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're willing to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.18,1:20:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.18,1:20:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you wait for.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.18,1:20:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.18,1:20:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.85,1:20:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.85,1:20:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.85,1:20:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.27,1:20:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to say thank you both for being here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.22,1:20:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.22,1:20:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.22,1:20:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.22,1:20:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.22,1:21:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering what's the best way to increase my intuitive powers?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.89,1:21:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to increase your intuitive powers.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.89,1:21:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want to do is decrease your reliance on thinkingness itself and perception.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.89,1:21:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And ask God to reveal to you the answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.89,1:21:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I say, you know, when you step back, it's invitational.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.02,1:21:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a yin position.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.02,1:21:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're summoning forth divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.06,1:21:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,By your willingness to surrender, you're asking the Holy Spirit for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.02,1:21:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,By a miracle, you mean, what you mean is that the Holy Spirit recontextualizes it so you see it differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.02,1:21:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And because you see it differently, your motivation changes without you having to actually do anything, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.02,1:21:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So being responsive to that which is sort of revealed, it's like awareness comes on without going through the thinking track.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.30,1:21:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.26,1:21:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.26,1:21:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.26,1:21:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.73,1:22:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.61,1:22:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a very linear way of explaining non-linearity, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.03,1:22:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Higgins?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.03,1:22:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.55,1:22:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.84,1:22:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.84,1:22:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You talked about the difference between divine love and personal love.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.84,1:22:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.84,1:22:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And as a couple in a relationship, when they go over 500, does personal love change?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.89,1:22:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Does...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.44,1:22:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.44,1:22:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Personal love can be still at 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.48,1:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Impersonal love is at 540.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.53,1:22:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We were watching...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.53,1:22:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that music we sent away for 515?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.17,1:22:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shipop or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.17,1:22:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.00,1:22:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shipom.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.82,1:22:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Bebop or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.82,1:22:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.82,1:22:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shipom, shipom.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.82,1:22:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Doo-wop.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.82,1:22:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Doo-wop.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.82,1:22:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Doo-wop.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.82,1:22:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A little richer now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.14,1:22:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.14,1:23:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.14,1:23:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doo-wop calibrates at 515.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.14,1:23:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.14,1:23:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's very romantic.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.14,1:23:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just love.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.10,1:23:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's romantic love, which is 515.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.10,1:23:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, romantic love is very, very personal.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.10,1:23:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So you got to let go of a lot to get up to 540, which is impersonal love.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.10,1:23:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doo-wop had a certain wonderful magic romance to it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.10,1:23:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And what the young people of today are really missing is sort of sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.10,1:23:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The music they listen to is often calibrates at 90 or 110.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.10,1:23:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So they don't know what it is to be carried away with rapture on the dance floor, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.06,1:23:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,515.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.30,1:23:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So unconditional is 540.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.30,1:23:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.30,1:23:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's a lovingness towards all of life and all of its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.30,1:23:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost a divine state.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.30,1:23:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,From 540 to 570 is really sainthood and spontaneous miraculous begins to occur.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.52,1:24:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Father Pio was at 570.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.52,1:24:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.68,1:24:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Saintliness.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.03,1:24:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A great pope is at 570.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.07,1:24:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Dalai Lama is at around 570.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.89,1:24:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.97,1:24:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.97,1:24:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Laura.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.68,1:24:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.68,1:24:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't want the whole day to go by without me coming up here and thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.89,1:24:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this has been such an emotional day for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.89,1:24:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And also I wanted to know if I can look out at the audience because I was frightened last time I was here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.89,1:24:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really frightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.97,1:24:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And sitting in line, I wasn't frightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.31,1:24:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like all of a sudden the fear just wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.31,1:25:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I nearly just said that I didn't need to do this and let the day go by without doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.31,1:25:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just couldn't not face the challenge today.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.47,1:25:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I just, something in me needed to come up here and...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.47,1:25:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcend that fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.56,1:25:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.56,1:25:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And also I needed to come up here to get a picture of this day.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.60,1:25:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was no way to go back.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.64,1:25:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't let it go by without getting up here to get a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.60,1:25:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody had a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.60,1:25:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I felt like if I let it go by without having a picture, I would have missed the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.60,1:25:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, so.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.60,1:25:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.60,1:25:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.60,1:25:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.60,1:25:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.77,1:25:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.44,1:25:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.44,1:25:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.47,1:25:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.47,1:25:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.47,1:25:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.47,1:25:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.47,1:25:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.47,1:25:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I just went out to sea with you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.47,1:25:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.43,1:25:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way we used to do it out at sea when the women weren't around, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.43,1:26:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.50,1:26:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.97,1:26:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a different story.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.97,1:26:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.97,1:26:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a privilege and an honor, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.97,1:26:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.97,1:26:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.97,1:26:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,On a personal note, I've had some kind of real upheaval in my personal life in the last couple of years.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.97,1:26:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.93,1:26:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been, shall we say, emotionally traumatic, and I harbor a certain amount of bitterness.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.93,1:26:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just wondering if you could give me some suggestions on how to get to a place of forgiveness and forgiving other people.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.93,1:26:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to dissect the bitterness you see as to its confluence.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.96,1:26:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.96,1:26:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're angry at a person or events.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.31,1:26:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.31,1:26:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.31,1:26:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've got to be more angry.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.34,1:26:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to assign yourself 6 o'clock every night you are going to have anger, period.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.34,1:26:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.34,1:27:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In that period, I want you to be angry and hate that person and fight them and skewer them and scream hatred at them.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.50,1:27:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.50,1:27:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And do it to the full extent.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.50,1:27:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.50,1:27:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No holding back.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.50,1:27:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just lay on the floor and writhe with anger and resentment.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.50,1:27:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.50,1:27:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,More, more, more, more.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.50,1:27:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.50,1:27:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And keep doing that until you run out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.50,1:27:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.64,1:27:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that just anchor, anchor, anger more into me?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.64,1:27:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.64,1:27:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.64,1:27:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what you're feeling now is a stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.64,1:27:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at an impasse.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.64,1:27:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.64,1:27:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I recognize that, you know, somebody says, well, forgiveness is a gift you give to yourself, but. . .
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.64,1:27:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, those are all jargon.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.64,1:27:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.64,1:27:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are all. . .
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.64,1:27:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just. . .
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.64,1:27:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.64,1:27:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to. . .
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.64,1:27:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just. . .
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.64,1:27:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand getting angry, but how is that going to get me to forgiveness?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.64,1:27:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because forgiveness is, it seems, light years away.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.64,1:27:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, first it's anger.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.64,1:27:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is the anger about?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.14,1:27:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfairness or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.14,1:27:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayal at the deepest levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.14,1:28:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayal?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.14,1:28:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Like spousal betrayal?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.14,1:28:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even deeper than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.14,1:28:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even deeper.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.14,1:28:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.14,1:28:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, my spouse betrayed me, and then she turned my own mother against me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.14,1:28:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.14,1:28:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.14,1:28:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's pretty common.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.56,1:28:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.81,1:28:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They do it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.81,1:28:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.81,1:28:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a paranoid who has delusions of infidelity.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.81,1:28:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother convinces you, your mother, that you've been out whoring around with every woman in town, where actually you haven't.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.77,1:28:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And your mother turns against you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.64,1:28:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.64,1:28:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.64,1:28:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't me that was doing the whoring.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.64,1:28:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my ex-wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.40,1:28:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the stories, you see how they propagate.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.47,1:28:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the end, they don't amount to anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.47,1:28:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the relationship is either based on something of a different level or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.47,1:28:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it's not, then there's no loss.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.53,1:29:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So nobody's convinced somebody else. . .
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.50,1:29:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worried about other people.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.50,1:29:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got their own drama.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.50,1:29:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They can keep their drama.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.50,1:29:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what is your problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.50,1:29:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I still got bitterness.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.50,1:29:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.50,1:29:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get out of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.50,1:29:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.50,1:29:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,About having total faith and trust and love in a person.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.50,1:29:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.50,1:29:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it appeared like they just turned around and stabbed me in the back.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.50,1:29:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How did they stab you in the back?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.50,1:29:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't want to get in a whole long therapy session, but I was married to a woman for 18 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.39,1:29:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.39,1:29:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she ran off with another guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.35,1:29:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And broke up my family.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.35,1:29:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all it is?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.35,1:29:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And destroyed the lives of my children?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.35,1:29:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife ran off with another guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.35,1:29:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, but it's not just that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.35,1:29:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She destroyed the lives of our children and our family.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.35,1:29:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I knew her family was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.35,1:29:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.35,1:29:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And then my relationship with my mother is destroyed, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.35,1:29:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God. Everything fell to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.35,1:29:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to complain.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.35,1:29:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to get to forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.35,1:29:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get to forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.35,1:29:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.13,1:29:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.13,1:29:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.13,1:29:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, because it's unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.80,1:30:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.84,1:30:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So that I can move on in my, I don't know, my higher levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.80,1:30:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're stuck in a resentment, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.80,1:30:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.80,1:30:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're stuck in a resentment.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.80,1:30:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.80,1:30:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to move beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.80,1:30:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think she's karmic payback, Mr. Playboy?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.80,1:30:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.80,1:30:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think so?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.80,1:30:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been Fidel in this all your lifetime?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.80,1:30:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.80,1:30:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not in this lifetime, but it could be in previous.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.80,1:30:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it wasn't in this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.22,1:30:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.22,1:30:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't in this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.22,1:30:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it seems unjust.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.22,1:30:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're paying back for something.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.14,1:30:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, I ask God to reveal to me, you know, the value of this experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.10,1:30:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're paying back something.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.13,1:30:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good karma that you're experiencing right now, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.13,1:30:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but it may...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.26,1:30:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let me tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.26,1:30:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in some lifetimes, you were an SOB.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.26,1:30:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You whored around and really broke all kinds of hearts.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.26,1:30:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.02,1:30:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first man in life who didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.02,1:31:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all animals at one time.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.71,1:31:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.97,1:31:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So you think this is my bad karma catching up with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.57,1:31:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Karma catching up with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.53,1:31:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's some kind of karmic undoing, just my guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.53,1:31:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the right to ask this, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.53,1:31:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have the right to ask this?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.53,1:31:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to ask this as a teaching example?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.53,1:31:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's undoing what he himself has done.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.60,1:31:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.36,1:31:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When something happens to you that you've totally unearned in this lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.36,1:31:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's coming from elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.36,1:31:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm paying karmic debt for my previous lifetime?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.36,1:31:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.36,1:31:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.36,1:31:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget, we're evolving up.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.36,1:31:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In past lifetimes, you weren't exactly a sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.32,1:31:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us were.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.32,1:31:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, we're not where we are because we came down from there.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.32,1:31:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here because we came up from there, you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.32,1:31:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so in this you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.32,1:31:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, I don't know what this means, but I surrender to this experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.32,1:31:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask your help to overcome this bitterness.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.32,1:32:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The bitterness is because I don't understand it from a larger context.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.32,1:32:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask the Holy Spirit for a miracle to recontextualize it so I see it as it is in truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.52,1:32:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.42,1:32:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The things of that depth and that pain don't come about for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.42,1:32:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the undoing of something, and you've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.46,1:32:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you're in another body, you totally blank out on the previous lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.46,1:32:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.46,1:32:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to suppose the likelihood is of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.00,1:32:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you learn past life recall techniques, you could probably go back there and re-experience it out,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.00,1:32:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's a nicety.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.00,1:32:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just take my word for it that it's very likely that this is not happening for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.96,1:32:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.96,1:32:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's serving some karmic purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.96,1:32:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also a lesson for the other people involved.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.96,1:32:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the only one involved in this little drama.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.96,1:32:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.96,1:32:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like psychodrama in which everybody is learning something.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.96,1:33:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I know she's got her own karma to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.96,1:33:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.96,1:33:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So what can I do to further evolve my karma to good karma in this lifetime?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.96,1:33:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just constantly surrender and forgive yourself for any negative feelings you have,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.96,1:33:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're only human, naturally you're going to have a resentment.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.96,1:33:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.92,1:33:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And forgive yourself for that and stop feeling guilty about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.92,1:33:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.92,1:33:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, I surrender it to God and ask God to see it differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.36,1:33:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrender to God and ask...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.36,1:33:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask God to see it differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.36,1:33:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask to see it differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.36,1:33:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask to see it in a larger context.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.36,1:33:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In a larger context.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.36,1:33:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.50,1:33:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you get a chance, you can go into past life recall.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.50,1:33:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,People teach hypnotic techniques.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.50,1:33:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you go back into past life, it'll rerun.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.50,1:33:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,See, past life is not like a memory like you saw that movie yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.46,1:33:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Past life, like going into your astral body, you reenter that time dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.46,1:33:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And that lifetime begins to... that runs again as a current reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.46,1:33:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You re-experience the thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.46,1:33:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you understand very well why it's all coming about.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.46,1:34:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.46,1:34:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.46,1:34:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.46,1:34:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very interesting experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.46,1:34:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You find somebody teaches self-hypnosis and does past life recall.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.46,1:34:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.52,1:34:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.52,1:34:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've actually read books on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.52,1:34:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a subject that interests me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.52,1:34:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.47,1:34:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It might...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.47,1:34:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be driven to that just, you know, for the sake of undoing this one thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.57,1:34:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.57,1:34:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.57,1:34:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.57,1:34:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than your life going to hell and your life being totally family destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.57,1:34:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's really not too bad, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.57,1:34:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.57,1:34:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.57,1:34:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great life just to be here with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.57,1:34:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes it all worth it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.57,1:34:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.42,1:34:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.42,1:34:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think most of us in the room have been in a really bad situation at one time or another.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.38,1:34:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people here have been in a really baddie?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.27,1:34:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That helps.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.27,1:35:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people have never gone through a real baddie?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.14,1:35:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No weirdos here, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.18,1:35:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty universal to go through a real crusher at least once every lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.18,1:35:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the fact that we're spiritually evolving tends to bring it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.23,1:35:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It brings it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.23,1:35:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.23,1:35:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To live it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.23,1:35:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.23,1:35:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to check in with the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.23,1:35:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.19,1:35:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.19,1:35:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.19,1:35:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.32,1:35:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.32,1:35:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.67,1:35:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, everybody here has been through a crusher.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.67,1:35:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's the price of one lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.73,1:35:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go back, but you're going to have to go through a bad crusher.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.92,1:35:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the you know what in the ringer.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.92,1:35:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.88,1:35:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Leg in the ringer.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.88,1:35:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I might briefly run a couple things past you that I've been going through spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.15,1:36:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In meditation, I seem to be finding spent a lot of time in meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.31,1:36:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And lately I'm hitting a like a black wall that it's really a comfortable, safe place where I always feel like I'm coming out of it, knowing something I didn't know when I was there.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.35,1:36:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So it makes me wonder.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.35,1:36:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand the immense immensity of the void itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.38,1:36:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know that there are numerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.38,1:36:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's not the void.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.38,1:36:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there numerous voids you go through?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.38,1:36:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.38,1:36:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just a blank.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.50,1:36:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a good space.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.50,1:36:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a very it's a very nice place.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.50,1:36:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It just keeps showing up.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.50,1:36:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And and I just kind of hang out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.50,1:36:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll keep going further into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.50,1:36:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.50,1:36:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And we never see you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.50,1:36:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the void.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.97,1:36:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this fabulous tool that I've been using from the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.02,1:36:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.97,1:36:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ, Christ guidance and Christ control.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.97,1:36:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.97,1:37:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in the Course in Miracles to hand things over to Christ guidance.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.97,1:37:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And when when it's too much to hand it over to Christ control, I don't hear much talk of this often.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.77,1:37:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any any view on that at all?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.00,1:37:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not a term I'm familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.00,1:37:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.44,1:37:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.44,1:37:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender to God is the general term.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.44,1:37:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.44,1:37:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to say that surrender has been the most powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.44,1:37:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.40,1:37:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tool that I've used since I started reading your books, which started it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.40,1:37:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you very much, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.40,1:37:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.40,1:37:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.47,1:37:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just feel so overwhelmed with the love of this experience and not just yours, but these people are so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.47,1:38:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And what prompted me to come up because I was feeling very happy to stay in my chair.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.72,1:38:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I decided to come up because I'm a mother of three children.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.72,1:38:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you were talking about the brainwashing in the media and in society and the calibrations of our universities now, it is very dismaying.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.93,1:38:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wondered if you might have some words of hope or counsel to a parent.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.93,1:38:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.89,1:38:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a jungle.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.35,1:38:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a jungle out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.35,1:38:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.35,1:38:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.35,1:38:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a great time to have children, I don't think, for that very reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.10,1:38:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going to send them to school?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.10,1:38:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you going to counter what you know is coming?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.10,1:38:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.81,1:38:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.60,1:38:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would you go?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.60,1:38:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would you live?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.60,1:38:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would you send them to school?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.02,1:39:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What I do is I calibrate the various universities and schools to see which ones calibrate the highest.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.10,1:39:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.10,1:39:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What else could you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.77,1:39:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I would try to educate them in advance so that they watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.77,1:39:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They become the observer-witness instead of the victim of that kind of thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.85,1:39:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What about being a parent before World War II and all the Nazi youth are being indoctrinated with fascist ideology?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.53,1:39:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like Boy Scout camp.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.53,1:39:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They all go camaraderie and they all repeat these mantras, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.50,1:39:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and die for their fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.61,1:39:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you had children?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.61,1:39:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That depends on how important they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.11,1:39:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be important enough that when you saw the way things were going,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.11,1:39:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you would leave the culture.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.11,1:39:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people did.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.11,1:39:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They lived in Germany and did not want to be indoctrinated.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.47,1:40:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's very difficult being a parent right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.61,1:40:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I would calibrate the various options and see what is possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.15,1:40:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.15,1:40:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.11,1:40:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take private school probably, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.11,1:40:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In the old days, people used to have tutors that taught them in various subjects, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.11,1:40:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want to be learned or you want a degree.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.11,1:40:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two different things.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.11,1:40:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be having all kinds of degrees and not be very learned.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.11,1:40:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, more dumb professors I've ever met in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.11,1:40:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can be a scholar on yourself and be well-versed and brilliant without a degree.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.11,1:40:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to decide, is a degree important?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.11,1:40:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, in what field?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.11,1:40:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it depends on what you want to go into.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.07,1:40:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Some fields you have to have a degree.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.07,1:40:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So in that case, you're going there to get the degree
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.14,1:40:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're aware that the learning is going to be limited and slanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.14,1:40:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So to know it in advance, it protects you from it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.38,1:41:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just listen to all kinds of propaganda and not be brainwashed
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.38,1:41:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,because I recognize that it's propaganda when I spot it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.38,1:41:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So a highly intelligent person who's aware of that could spot,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.98,1:41:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the programming coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.98,1:41:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see them on television.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.94,1:41:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They talk like people that are brainwashed talk in a brainwashed talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.97,1:41:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell the minute they're like in a hypnotic state,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.97,1:41:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,a mechanical repetition of that which they've been programmed.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.97,1:41:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can spot it in an instant like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.01,1:41:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's hard being a parent right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.77,1:41:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.77,1:41:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very tough era to be a parent.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.36,1:41:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She inspired me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.39,1:41:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.39,1:41:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time I came up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.39,1:41:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My ego came up and then I froze.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.39,1:41:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.39,1:41:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just wanted to face the fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.39,1:41:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.39,1:41:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.39,1:41:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.39,1:42:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're letting the fear about fear for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.97,1:42:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You just let yourself be scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.97,1:42:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.97,1:42:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not scared enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.97,1:42:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You let yourself be more and more and more scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.97,1:42:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, you can say, oh, the hell with it, and you quit being scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.97,1:42:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you faced it up today.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.97,1:42:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.97,1:42:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.97,1:42:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.03,1:42:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're great.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.03,1:42:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good courage for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.22,1:42:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stage fright is a scary one.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.93,1:42:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen your audience.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.02,1:42:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, but the unconscious fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.02,1:42:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.02,1:42:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.02,1:42:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was also inspired to face my fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.02,1:42:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.02,1:42:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.02,1:42:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.02,1:42:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is I work closely with a woman who seems to be dealing with a lot of grief.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.10,1:42:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.10,1:42:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is in her best interest when that comes up?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.30,1:42:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the best way to react?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.30,1:42:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what is best?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.26,1:42:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your relationship with her?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.26,1:42:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm her caregiver.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.26,1:42:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, caregiver.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.26,1:42:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.26,1:42:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.26,1:43:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you help her through it as to decompress it as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.30,1:43:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her weep it out and experience it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.52,1:43:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you try to take her to acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.52,1:43:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.57,1:43:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a hard time moving from sympathy to empathy.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.57,1:43:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like she brings up a lot of emotion in me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.57,1:43:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.57,1:43:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.00,1:43:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.00,1:43:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Get another job.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.00,1:43:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.34,1:43:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Broccoli would say.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.93,1:43:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.93,1:43:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.93,1:43:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Broccoli say?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.14,1:43:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What would Broccoli say?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.14,1:43:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.14,1:43:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.14,1:43:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.14,1:43:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.02,1:43:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.22,1:43:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.22,1:43:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.22,1:43:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult what her role should be, you know, and how much she can help that person
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.77,1:43:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and how much she can be of help to that person.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.77,1:43:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, compassionate companionship in itself is very valuable that somebody cares enough
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.77,1:43:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,for you to help you live through the experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.72,1:44:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And somebody asked that we finish it up with a prayer today in line with the devotional
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.72,1:44:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.72,1:44:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, I thought that which is the voice of God is silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.76,1:44:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That we sink into the voice of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.07,1:44:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We sink into the silence which is indicative of divine presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.07,1:44:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind the thought, behind the thinkingness is an infinite silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.46,1:44:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And the infinite silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.93,1:44:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the source of all existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.60,1:44:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And between the thoughts, under the thoughts is the profound silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.34,1:44:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And all we have to do is become aware of that silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.35,1:45:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is become aware of that silence by realizing it's there.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.10,1:46:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind all the sound of the universe, the silence is forever there.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.88,1:46:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind the sounds in the woods, in the woods are silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.69,1:46:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of the bird doesn't have anything to do with the silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.60,1:46:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the silence is maintained even though there's sound above it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.10,1:46:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But the only reason you can hear the sound is because it's against the background of silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.10,1:46:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So the silence is there right in the middle of sound.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.42,1:46:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So you focus on the silence which is ever-present.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.28,1:46:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of cacophony and catastrophe as the bullets are flying around and the planes are crashing
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.28,1:46:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and all hell is breaking loose.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.25,1:46:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing but the infinite silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.60,1:46:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you identify with that silence and just maintain the awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.60,1:46:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go about your daily life and do everything that you need to do
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.60,1:46:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and at all times still be aware of the presence of the silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.81,1:47:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So that gives you a centering.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.92,1:47:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So a centering kind of prayerfulness is you're always aware of the silence,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.05,1:47:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the infinite context.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.05,1:47:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The reality of the presence of God is an infinite silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.52,1:47:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you hold in mind in that silence tends to manifest.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.89,1:47:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as a result of causation, but potentiality manifesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.02,1:47:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And we thank Thee, O Lord, for Thy divine presence
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.52,1:47:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,as the infinite silence out of which arises our existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.26,1:47:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.68,1:47:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that was some pretty fancy prayer, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.28,1:48:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my joy to be with you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.02,1:48:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I look forward to our next meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.02,1:48:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And we finish with the same we started, Gloria in excelsis Deo.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.02,1:48:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We thank Thee, O Lord, for Thy divine presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.14,1:48:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.75,1:48:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my gift from God.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.75,1:48:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.06,1:48:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here is my presence from God.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.50,1:48:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.17,1:48:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.00,1:48:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.00,1:48:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at these gorgeous flowers.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.00,1:48:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.00,1:48:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gorgeous, aren't they?
